        "label": "PER",
        "start": 3,
        "end": 6
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000139",
    "sentence": "及按慎矜，鉉先與張瑄同臺，情旨素厚，貴取媚於權臣，誣瑄與楊慎矜共解圖讖。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "楊慎矜",
        "label": "PER",
        "start": 28,
        "end": 31
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000140",
    "sentence": "持之，為驢駒板橛以成其獄。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000141",
    "sentence": "又為王鉷閑廄判官，鉷緣邢縡事朝堂被推，鉉證云：「大夫將白帖索廄馬五百匹以助逆，我不與之。」鉷死在晷刻，鉉忍誣之，眾咸怒恨焉。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "大夫",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 24,
        "end": 26
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000142",
    "sentence": "及被貶為廬江長史，在郡忽見瑄為祟，乃云：「端公何得來乞命？不自由。」鉉須臾而卒。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "在郡",
        "label": "LOC",
        "start": 9,
        "end": 11
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000143",
    "sentence": "羅希奭",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "羅希奭",
        "label": "PER",
        "start": 0,
        "end": 3
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000144",
    "sentence": "羅希奭，本杭州人也，近家洛陽，鴻臚少卿張博濟堂外甥。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "羅希奭",
        "label": "PER",
        "start": 0,
        "end": 3
      },
      {
        "text": "本杭州",
        "label": "LOC",
        "start": 4,
        "end": 7
      },
      {
        "text": "洛陽",
        "label": "LOC",
        "start": 12,
        "end": 14
      },
      {
        "text": "張博濟",
        "label": "PER",
        "start": 19,
        "end": 22
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000145",
    "sentence": "為吏持法深刻。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000146",
    "sentence": "天寶初，右相李林甫引與吉溫持獄，又與希奭姻婭，自御史臺主簿再遷殿中侍御史。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "李林甫",
        "label": "PER",
        "start": 6,
        "end": 9
      },
      {
        "text": "御史",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 24,
        "end": 26
      },
      {
        "text": "御史",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 34,
        "end": 36
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000147",
    "sentence": "自韋堅、皇甫惟明、李適之、柳勣、裴敦復、李邕、鄔元昌、楊慎矜、趙奉璋下獄事，皆與溫鍛煉，故時稱「羅鉗吉網」，惡其深刻也。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "皇甫惟明",
        "label": "PER",
        "start": 4,
        "end": 8
      },
      {
        "text": "李適之",
        "label": "PER",
        "start": 9,
        "end": 12
      },
      {
        "text": "裴敦復",
        "label": "PER",
        "start": 16,
        "end": 19
      },
      {
        "text": "楊慎矜",
        "label": "PER",
        "start": 27,
        "end": 30
      },
      {
        "text": "趙奉璋",
        "label": "PER",
        "start": 31,
        "end": 34
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000148",
    "sentence": "八載，除刑部員外，轉郎中。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000149",
    "sentence": "十一載，李林甫卒，出為中部、始安二太守，仍充當管經略使。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "李林甫",
        "label": "PER",
        "start": 4,
        "end": 7
      },
      {
        "text": "太守",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 17,
        "end": 19
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000150",
    "sentence": "十四載，以張博濟、吉溫，韋陟、韋誡奢、李從一、員錫等流貶，皆於始安，希奭或令假攝。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "張博濟",
        "label": "PER",
        "start": 5,
        "end": 8
      },
      {
        "text": "韋誡奢",
        "label": "PER",
        "start": 15,
        "end": 18
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000151",
    "sentence": "右相楊國忠奏遣司直蔣沇往按之，復令張光奇替為始安太守。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "楊國忠",
        "label": "PER",
        "start": 2,
        "end": 5
      },
      {
        "text": "張光奇",
        "label": "PER",
        "start": 17,
        "end": 20
      },
      {
        "text": "太守",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 24,
        "end": 26
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000152",
    "sentence": "仍降敕曰：",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000153",
    "sentence": "前始安郡太守、充當管經略使羅希奭，幸此資序，叨居牧守。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "前始安郡",
        "label": "LOC",
        "start": 0,
        "end": 4
      },
      {
        "text": "太守",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 4,
        "end": 6
      },
      {
        "text": "羅希奭",
        "label": "PER",
        "start": 13,
        "end": 16
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000154",
    "sentence": "地列要荒，人多竄殛，尤加委任，冀絕奸訛。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000155",
    "sentence": "翻乃嘯結逋逃，群聚不逞，應是流貶，公然安置。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000156",
    "sentence": "或差攝郡縣，割剝黎氓；或輟借館宇，侵擾人吏。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "或差攝郡縣",
        "label": "LOC",
        "start": 0,
        "end": 5
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000157",
    "sentence": "不唯輕侮典憲，實亦隳壞紀綱。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000158",
    "sentence": "擢發數愆，豈多其罪，可貶海東郡海康尉、員外置。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "可貶海東郡",
        "label": "LOC",
        "start": 10,
        "end": 15
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000159",
    "sentence": "張博濟往托回邪，跡惟憑恃，嘗自抵犯，又坐親姻，前後貶官，歲月頗久，逗留不赴，情狀難容。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "張博濟",
        "label": "PER",
        "start": 0,
        "end": 3
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000160",
    "sentence": "及命按舉，仍更潛匿，亡命逭刑，莫斯為甚。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000161",
    "sentence": "並當切害，合峻常刑，宜於所在各決重杖六十。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000162",
    "sentence": "使夫為政之士，克守章程；負罪之人，期於悛革。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000163",
    "sentence": "凡厥在位，宜各悉心。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000164",
    "sentence": "時員錫、李從一、韋誡奢、吉承恩並決杖，遣司直宇文審往監之。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "韋誡奢",
        "label": "PER",
        "start": 8,
        "end": 11
      },
      {
        "text": "宇文審",
        "label": "PER",
        "start": 22,
        "end": 25
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000165",
    "sentence": "毛若虛",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000166",
    "sentence": "毛若虛，絳州太平人也。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "絳州",
        "label": "LOC",
        "start": 4,
        "end": 6
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000167",
    "sentence": "眉毛覆於眼，其性殘忍。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000168",
    "sentence": "初為蜀川縣尉，使司以推勾見任。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "初為蜀川縣",
        "label": "LOC",
        "start": 0,
        "end": 5
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000169",
    "sentence": "天寶末，為武功丞，年已六十餘矣。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000170",
    "sentence": "肅宗收兩京，除監察御史。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "御史",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 9,
        "end": 11
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000171",
    "sentence": "審國用不足，上策徵剝財貨。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000172",
    "sentence": "有潤於公者，日有進奉，漸見任用稱旨。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000173",
    "sentence": "每推一人，未鞫，即先收其家資，以定贓數。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000174",
    "sentence": "不滿望，即攤徵鄉里近親。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "即攤徵鄉",
        "label": "LOC",
        "start": 4,
        "end": 8
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000175",
    "sentence": "峻其威權，人皆懼死，輸納不差晷刻。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000176",
    "sentence": "乾元二年 ，鳳翔府七坊押官先行剽劫，州縣不能制，因有劫殺事。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "二年",
        "label": "TME",
        "start": 2,
        "end": 4
      },
      {
        "text": "州縣",
        "label": "LOC",
        "start": 18,
        "end": 20
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000177",
    "sentence": "縣尉謝夷甫因眾怒，遂搒殺之。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "謝夷甫",
        "label": "PER",
        "start": 2,
        "end": 5
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000178",
    "sentence": "其妻訴於李輔國，輔國奏請御史孫瑩鞫之。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "李輔國",
        "label": "PER",
        "start": 4,
        "end": 7
      },
      {
        "text": "御史",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 12,
        "end": 14
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000179",
    "sentence": "瑩不能正其事。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000180",
    "sentence": "又令中丞崔伯陽三司使雜訊之，又不證成其罪。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "崔伯陽",
        "label": "PER",
        "start": 4,
        "end": 7
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000181",
    "sentence": "因令若虛推之，遂歸罪於夷甫。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000182",
    "sentence": "伯陽與之言，若虛頗不遜。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000183",
    "sentence": "伯陽數讓之，若虛馳謁告急。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000184",
    "sentence": "肅宗曰：「卿且出。」對曰：「臣出即死矣。」肅宗潛留若虛簾內，召伯陽至，伯陽頗短若虛。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000185",
    "sentence": "上怒，叱出之。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000186",
    "sentence": "因流貶伯陽同推官十餘人，皆於嶺外遠惡處。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000187",
    "sentence": "宰相李峴以左右於瑩等，亦被貶斥。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000188",
    "sentence": "於是若虛威震朝列，公卿懾懼矣！",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000189",
    "sentence": "尋擢為御史中丞。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "御史",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 3,
        "end": 5
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000190",
    "sentence": "上元元年 ，貶賓化尉而死。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "元年",
        "label": "TME",
        "start": 2,
        "end": 4
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000191",
    "sentence": "敬羽 〈 裴升　畢曜附 〉",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000192",
    "sentence": "敬羽，寶鼎人也。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000193",
    "sentence": "父昭道，開元初為監察御史。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "元",
        "label": "ORG",
        "start": 5,
        "end": 6
      },
      {
        "text": "御史",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 10,
        "end": 12
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000194",
    "sentence": "羽貌寢而性便僻，善候人意旨。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000195",
    "sentence": "天寶九載，為康成縣尉。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "為康成縣",
        "label": "LOC",
        "start": 5,
        "end": 9
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000196",
    "sentence": "安思順為朔方節度使，引在幕下。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "安思順",
        "label": "PER",
        "start": 0,
        "end": 3
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000197",
    "sentence": "及肅宗於靈武即大位，羽尋擢為監察御史。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "御史",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 16,
        "end": 18
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000198",
    "sentence": "以苛刻徵剝求進。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000199",
    "sentence": "及收兩京後，轉見委任。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000200",
    "sentence": "作大枷，有鹴尾榆，著即悶絕。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000201",
    "sentence": "又臥囚於地，以門關輾其腹，號為「肉餺飥」。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "以門關",
        "label": "LOC",
        "start": 6,
        "end": 9
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000202",
    "sentence": "掘地為坑，實以棘刺，以敗席覆上，領囚臨坑訊之，必墜其中，萬刺攢之。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000203",
    "sentence": "又捕逐錢貨，不減毛若虛。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000204",
    "sentence": "上元中，擢為御史中丞。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "元",
        "label": "ORG",
        "start": 1,
        "end": 2
      },
      {
        "text": "御史",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 6,
        "end": 8
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000205",
    "sentence": "太子少傅、宗正卿、鄭國公李遵，為宗子通事舍人李若冰告其贓私，詔羽按之。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "太子",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 0,
        "end": 2
      },
      {
        "text": "李若冰",
        "label": "PER",
        "start": 22,
        "end": 25
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000206",
    "sentence": "羽延遵，各危坐於小床。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000207",
    "sentence": "羽小瘦，遵豐碩，頃間問即倒，請垂足。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000208",
    "sentence": "羽曰：「尚書下獄是囚，羽禮延坐，何得慢耶！」遵絕倒者數四。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "尚書",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 4,
        "end": 6
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000209",
    "sentence": "請問，羽徐應之，授紙筆，書贓數千貫，奏之。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000210",
    "sentence": "肅宗以勛舊舍之，但停宗正卿。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000211",
    "sentence": "及嗣薛王珍潛謀不軌，詔羽鞫之。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000212",
    "sentence": "羽召支黨羅於廷，索鹴尾榆枷之，布栲訊之具以繞之，信宿成獄。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000213",
    "sentence": "珍坐死，右衛將軍竇如玢、試都水使者崔昌等九人並斬，太子洗馬趙非熊、陳王府長史陳閎、楚州司馬張昴、左武衛兵曹參軍焦自榮，前鳳翔府郿縣主簿李 ⿱ 、廣文館進士張夐等六人決殺，駙馬都尉薛履謙賜自盡，左散騎常侍張鎬貶辰州司戶。",
