      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000227",
    "sentence": "贊曰：王德將衰，政在奸臣。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000228",
    "sentence": "鷹犬搏擊，縱之者人。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_186c_000229",
    "sentence": "遭其毒螫，可為悲辛。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
